Paper: hep-th/0103165

Date: 2001-03-20

Title: Comments on Born-Infeld Theory

Authors: John H. Schwarz

Comments: 10 pages; talk presented at Strings 2001

The low-energy effective action of supersymmetric D-brane systems consists oftwo terms, one of which is of the Born-Infeld type and one of which is of theChern-Simons type. I briefly review the status of our understanding of theseterms for both the Abelian and non-Abelian cases.